title: /usr/bin/ld: warning: libcudart.so.8.0, needed by //usr/local/lib/libnccl.so.1, not found (try using -rpath or -rpath-link)
body_html:
Username:
Linux chandu 4.15.0-24-generic #26~16.04.1-Ubuntu SMP Fri Jun 15 14:35:08 UTC 2018 x86_64 x86_64 x86_64 GNU/Linux

This is the process I have followed:
https://caffe2.ai/docs/getting-started.html?platform=ubuntu&configuration=compile

1).
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends
build-essential
cmake
git
libgoogle-glog-dev
libgtest-dev
libiomp-dev
libleveldb-dev
liblmdb-dev
libopencv-dev
libopenmpi-dev
libsnappy-dev
libprotobuf-dev
openmpi-bin
openmpi-doc
protobuf-compiler
python-dev
python-pip

pip install --user
future
numpy
protobuf

  1. sudo apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends libgflags-dev

  2. git clone --recursive https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch.git && cd pytorch

  3. git submodule update --init

  4. mkdir build && cd build

  5. cmake ..
